    "Claim that the email was internal work is refuted by the external headhunter domain headhunter-corp.com and subject 薪资数据参考.",
    "IT-SEC-2026-INV-042 scope limitation resolved: the report covered cloud sharing, shared links, and guest access, while the leak path was email attachment.",
    "Claim that the file was modified before sending is refuted by the byte-identical hash match."
  ],
  "conclusion": {
    "verdict": "confirmed data breach via external email attachment",
    "confidence": "high"
  },
  "recommended_actions": [
    "Immediately revoke or suspend 林小雅's access to salary files, HR shared drives, and external email attachment privileges pending formal handling.",
    "Initiate formal disciplinary and legal review procedures with HR leadership, Legal, and Compliance using the preserved evidence chain.",
    "Preserve original email headers, attachment binaries, cloud access logs, and forensic metadata outputs in a restricted evidence repository.",
    "Assess notification and mitigation obligations for affected employees, including the v1.1 additions 李明, 赵伟, and 孙丽.",
    "Implement technical controls for payroll files, including DLP rules for external attachments, watermarking, download alerts, and stricter approval workflows."
  ]
}

